=== Site-wide === <!--T:159-->
</translate>
<translate><!--T:160--> The standard #, ##, ### wikitext can be used alongside CSS in [[MediaWiki:Common.css]] to produce the usual system of numbered lists (1, 2, 3; then a, b, c; then i, ii, iii):</translate>

<syntaxhighlight lang="css">
ol {
	list-style-type: decimal;
}
ol li > ol {
	list-style-type: lower-alpha;
}
ol li > ol li > ol {
	list-style-type: lower-roman;
}
</syntaxhighlight>

<translate><!--T:161--> The first <tvar name=1><code>ol</code></tvar> above is the default, so not necessary unless some other list-style-type is required.</translate>

{| class="wikitable"
!<translate><!--T:162--> Wikitext</translate>
!<translate><!--T:163--> Rendering</translate>
|-
|
<pre>
#list item A1
##list item B1
###list item C1
###list item C2
##list item B2
#list item A2
</pre>
|
<ol style="list-style-type: decimal"><li>list item A1
<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha"><li>list item B1
<ol style="list-style-type: lower-roman"><li>list item C1</li>
<li>list item C2</li></ol>
<li>list item B2</li></ol></li>
<li>list item A2</li></ol>
|}

